  hex_session_ids allows you to change the radix of session identifiers
  displayed in the various IMA tables from decimal to hexadecimal.

  IMA columns affected by setting this for a DBMS server are:

      ima_server_sessions.session_ptr
      ima_server_sessions.session_id

      ima_server_sessions_desc.session_id

      ima_server_sessions_extra.session_id

      ima_locklists.locklist_session_id

      ima_log_processes.force_abort_session
      ima_log_processes.group_commit_session

      ima_log_transactions.tx_session_id

  IMA columns affected by setting this for an ICESVR are:

      ice_user_transactions.trn_session

